summary: 检测用友时空KSOA系统的PrintZPYG.jsp接口是否存在SQL注入漏洞，该漏洞可能允许黑客执行任意SQL语句，包括查询数据、下载数据、写入webshell等。
summary_en: Detect whether the PrintZPYG.jsp interface of Yonyou KSOA system has SQL injection vulnerability, which may allow hackers to execute arbitrary SQL statements, including querying data, downloading data, writing webshell, etc.
